(91, '1', '12', '61', '3', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">In order to perform a more proactive role in providing IT services, consider creating an Information Technology Steering Committee (ITSC) with defined objectives and scope, responsibility, accountability, reporting structure, and frequency of meetings. It is recommended that all division heads are involved in the proposed ITSC to formulate, prioritize and recommend to Management various programs/projects on IT. The possible duties and responsibilities of ITSC are as follows:</span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">Direct, review, and approve IT strategic plans;</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">Oversee the implementation of IT projects and allocate resources;&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">Connect end-users with the MIS Section to facilitate exchanges of&nbsp; users&rsquo; needs, priorities, and satisfaction levels; and</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">Recommend to Management policies/standards on issues/matters pertaining to IT.</span></li>\r\n</ul>', ' ', ' ', ' ', '2019-08-28 07:32:14', '2020-01-06 15:25:16', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' '),
(92, '1', '20', '62', '3', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 10pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Management should ensure that every employee shall be provided with a function computer to effectively and efficiently perform his or her job.</span></p>', ' ', ' ', ' ', '2019-08-28 07:35:05', '2020-01-06 15:25:16', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' '),
(94, '1', '14', '63', '3', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">The MIS Section should spearhead the crafting of ISSP and&nbsp; follow the ISSP Process Flow required by DICT which should include the following:&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">Conduct of ISSP workshop&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">Organization of the ISSP-Technical Working Group (TWG)</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">Assessment of organizational strategy</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">Formulation of IS development strategy</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">Conceptualization of ICT projects</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">Identification of resource requirements, and</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">Approval of the ISSP by the agency management</span></li>\r\n</ul>', ' ', ' ', ' ', '2019-08-28 07:39:18', '2020-01-06 15:25:16', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' '),
(95, '1', '24', '64', '3', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 10pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">For secured server room, ITDI may consider the following measures:</span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 10pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Install a fire extinguisher in the server room (e.g., Halocarbon, Halo 1211, and CO2);</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 10pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Provide safe distance between air conditioning units and servers or install water leak sensors;</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 10pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Invest in new programmable air conditioner that has temperature control system; and</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 10pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Use biometrics device to provide additional access control for the server room.</span></li>\r\n</ul>', ' ', ' ', ' ', '2019-08-28 07:41:21', '2020-01-06 15:25:16', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' '),
