(152, '1', '4', '88', '38', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Compliance with the IRR RA 9184 particularly on:</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Procurement Planning</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Detailed Engineering Design, TOR&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Preparation of Plans, Specifications and Estimates.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Procurement Process (Bidding)</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;Thorough evaluation of Bids,&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(Balanced Bids)</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Project Implementation</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Project Monitoring, evaluations of&nbsp;</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;VO/CO, Time Extensions and&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Delay payments.</span></p>', ' ', ' ', ' ', '2019-10-25 07:12:30', '2020-01-07 08:35:45', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' '),
(153, '1', '8', '59', '7', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Management should develop an IT organizational structure that clearly reflects its role in delivering the Institute\'s products and services and achieving its strategic goals; and<br /></span></p>', ' ', ' ', ' ', '2019-10-30 11:50:38', '2020-01-06 15:25:16', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' '),
(154, '1', '8', '59', '7', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Ensure that the agency-wide strategic plan should include IT, or there is a separate IT strategic plan, that addresses the technology needs of the agency, to effectively and efficiently meet its overall strategic plan.</span></span></p>', ' ', ' ', ' ', '2019-10-30 11:53:57', '2020-01-06 15:25:16', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' '),
(155, '1', '28', '89', '4', '<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">1. The ITDI should be a pioneer or lead innovator in its sectoral coveraage. The R&amp;D divisions should come-up with more strategic and purposive roadmaps similar to the Packaging Technology Division which could share how they were able to develop their roadmap with the other divisions.&nbsp; There are also similar&nbsp; published R&amp;D and technology roadmaps from other prestigious R&amp;D institutions which can be made as a reference. Example of which are the roadmaps prepared by ITRI which has similar sectors being covered, hence, these can be used as a benchmark.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">2. The ITDI could also develop a generic roadmapping process that could be used as a guide by the different divisions.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">3. Each distinct section in the division should come-up with a separate R&amp;D roadmap, i.e. Chemicals and Energy for the CED, and Environment and Biotechnology for EBD</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">4. Engagement of the stakeholders during the roadmap development process should be a necessary step and should be shown.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"text-align: justify;\">5. The roadmaps should be translated into an action plan that would be used as guide in the pursuit of research priorities and technology development of each division.</span></p>', ' ', ' ', ' ', '2019-10-30 15:32:21', '2020-01-06 15:25:16', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' '),
(156, '1', '42', '91', '4', '<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">CED should conduct monitoring and evaluation of the potential energy savings of the industries/institutions audited to understand which measures have been implemented to carry out if the activities were over or underestimated.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">Also, CED should consider targetting companies for the year which they wish to approach for audit to create significant impact to the industries it serves.</span></p>', ' ', ' ', ' ', '2019-11-06 17:06:55', '2020-01-06 15:25:16', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' '),
(157, '1', '3', '90', '2', '<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Revisit mandate especially after the Rat Plan to determine what defines&nbsp; and makes the role of ITDI in STI distinct to ensure its continuity especially with the upcoming government Rightsizing Program;&nbsp;</span></p>', ' ', ' ', ' ', '2019-12-12 18:18:41', '2020-01-07 08:35:45', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' '),
(158, '1', '3', '90', '2', '<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Look into&nbsp; how the organizational structure can be improved/strengthened for ITDI to quickly respond to changing industry needs;</span></p>', ' ', ' ', ' ', '2019-12-12 18:19:12', '2020-01-07 08:35:45', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' '),
(159, '1', '3', '90', '2', '<p>Evaluate functions, services, areas of coverage, processes and products vis-a-vis other organizations with similar f-s-a-p-p and see how ITDI can &ldquo;niche&rdquo; in the presence of these other interventions/ facilties.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', ' ', ' ', ' ', '2019-12-12 18:19:41', '2020-01-07 08:35:45', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' '),
(160, '1', '8', '92', '2', '<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Soul-search and brainstorm as an institute in consultation with the industries it serves on how ITDI can strategically position itself in the more important areas that the industries need assistance on, identifying the specific sectors, fields and technologies that need to be pursued and developed to become a more relevant and dynamic partner;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Involve the target industries in identifying specific areas that ITDI need to improve and expand on especially in the setting up of bigger facilities, STI centers of excellence, and services;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Have an outward focus, giving strong consideration of the competitive and market environment where ITDI operates; link with other government agecies like DTI, DOH-FDA, DENR, and LGUs to establish itself among the players supporting industries</span></p>', ' ', ' ', ' ', '2019-12-12 19:12:43', '2020-01-06 15:47:04', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' '),
(161, '1', '8', '92', '2', '<p>Determine and develop niches along its core competencies especially with its diverse industry concerns;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Study the competencies and capacities of its existing human resources and determine the gaps that need to be developed with timelines and budget considerations</p>', ' ', ' ', ' ', '2019-12-12 19:19:01', '2020-01-06 15:47:04', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' '),
(162, '1', '8', '92', '2', '<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Finalize the Strategic Plan and consult/validate the Plan with stakeholders/industries ITDI serves and the bigger S&amp;T community that it is part of;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Set in place a monitoring and evaluation mechanism to determine attainment of strategic objectives, goals and outcomes within the set timelines; and</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Consider/include the risk factors and the risk management plan in the Strategic Plan to ensure that the priority needs and risks/concerns are addressed because r</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">isks can potentially disrupt processes or can create disparities in the implementation of the strategies/goals of the plan.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', ' ', ' ', ' ', '2019-12-12 19:34:56', '2020-01-06 15:47:04', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' '),
(163, '1', '8', '93', '2', '<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Be a consistent provider of local technologies required by the SMES and even the medium enterprises in the country in line with its mission to contribute in making local industries globally competitive;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Continue to develop big impact projects such as the Food Innovation Center and follow-through technologies such as development of product prototypes from the FICs;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', ' ', ' ', ' ', '2019-12-12 19:53:01', '2020-01-07 08:35:45', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' '),
(164, '1', '8', '93', '2', '<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Link with other RDIs (e.g., MIRDC, PTRI, FNRI) to develop high value/more sophisticated&nbsp; technologies thru collaboration/convergence; and</span></p>', ' ', '2', ' ', '2019-12-12 19:57:15', '2020-01-07 08:35:45', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' '),
(165, '1', '8', '93', '2', '<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Develop a feedback mechanism from adopters, particularly from the regions through the Regional Offices, to ensure full diffision and utilization of ITDI developed technologies and maturity of technologies for roll-out; and&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Forge an efficient link and working relationship with the DOST Regional Offices through the Office of the Undersecretary for Regional Operations to be able to secure institutional support such as the information systems, funding, and other needed assistance.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', ' ', ' ', ' ', '2019-12-12 20:04:23', '2020-01-07 08:35:45', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' '),
(169, '1', '22', '70', '39', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 10pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">The MIS Section should identify obsolete computers (e.g., 3 yrs old and above) and make a corresponding request for replacement through MITHI funding;&nbsp; and include also in the ISSP the needed video editing and product design software of TSD.</span></p>', ' ', ' ', ' ', '2019-12-27 14:55:59', '2020-01-06 15:25:16', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' '),
(170, '1', '34', '76', '39', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 10pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">ITDI Management to implement a policy that all R&amp;D funded projects should have identified cooperators who may be interested in sharing the R&amp;D cost and/or adopt the research output in the future;</span></p>', ' ', ' ', ' ', '2019-12-27 15:17:33', '2020-01-06 15:25:16', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' '),
(171, '1', '34', '76', '39', '<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Establish linkages with cooperators who will serve as consumers/markets of the technologies; and</span></p>', ' ', ' ', ' ', '2019-12-27 15:18:08', '2020-01-06 15:25:16', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' '),
(172, '1', '34', '76', '39', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-size: 10pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Review the technology transfer process to strike a balance between the interests of the clients and the researchers.</span></p>', ' ', ' ', ' ', '2019-12-27 15:18:29', '2020-01-06 15:25:16', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' '),
(173, '1', '41', '86', '39', '<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">We recommend TSD to benchmark the M&amp;E process being implemented by FPRDI.</span></span></p>', ' ', ' ', ' ', '2019-12-27 15:32:49', '2020-01-06 15:25:16', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ', ' ');
