(13, '1', 9, '', '5', 'Administrative Management Division', ' ', 'Unfilled Plantilla Positions', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\"><strong>Numerous unfilled plantilla positions</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">Based on the Rationalization Plan of ITDI dated February 5, 2010, there are two hundred seventy-five (275) approved plantilla positions, excluding the ninety-four (94) positions deployed to Standards and Testing Division (50) and National Metrology Division (44) which are not covered in the audit. Of these 275 positions, twenty-eight (28) are unfilled as of June 30, 2018.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">Table __: Distribution of Pantilla Positions per Division</span></p>\r\n<table style=\"border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%;\" border=\"1\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 25%; text-align: center;\" rowspan=\"2\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">Office/Division</span></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 25%; text-align: center;\" colspan=\"2\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">No. of Plantilla Positions</span></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 25%; text-align: center;\" rowspan=\"2\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">Total</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 25%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">Filled</span></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 25%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">Unfilled</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 25%;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans