tica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">SRS II</span></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 16.6667%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">16</span></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 16.6667%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">PMISD</span></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 16.6667%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">PTD</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 16.6667%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">20</span></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 16.6667%;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">Basbasan, Jr., Angel T.</span></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 16.6667%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">SRS II</span></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 16.6667%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">16</span></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 16.6667%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">NMD</span></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 16.6667%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">PTD</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 16.6667%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">21</span></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 16.6667%;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">Baaco, Ricky B.</span></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 16.6667%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">Science Aide</span></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 16.6667%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">4</span></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 16.6667%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">FPD</span></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 16.6667%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">PTD</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">In addition to the audit criteria mentioned above, said EO explained that reassignment of personnel does not require the issuance of an appointment. However, this shall require an Office Order issued by the appointing officer/authority. Considering that the appointment is not station-specific, the employee concerned may request for a recall of the reassignment citing his/her reasons why he/she wants to go back to his/her original station.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">Upon comparing the PSIPOP and the actual assignments of the ITDI Personnel, it is observed that said all reassignments were not documented by Special Orders.</span></p>', '', ' ', ' ', ' ', '2019-08-15 08:50:59', '2019-08-16 14:49:28', '0', '1', ' '),
(18, '1', 17, '', '5', 'Administrative Management Division', ' ', 'Loyalty Award', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\"><strong>Non-monetary payments for Loyalty Award was not complied with</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">CSC Memorandum Circular No. 06, series of 2002, through CSC Resolution No. 02-0295 dated February 26, 2002, issued the Revised Guidelines on the Grant of Loyalty Award. These policies were formulated to recognize the continuous and satisfactory service rendered in the government by officials and employees for a period of ten (10) years. The said MC further provides that the awardee shall receive a loyalty memorabilla/souvenir as follows:</span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">10 and 15 years- bronze service pin;</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">20 and 25 years- silver service ring;</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">30, 35 and 40 years- gold service medallion; or</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">other memorabilla/souvenir as may be provided by the agency PRAISE Committee.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">In addition to this, a loyalty cash award (LCA) of the following amounts are required by COA Circular 2013-003A.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">Table __: Loyalty Cash Award</span></p>\r\n<table style=\"border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%;\" border=\"1\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\"><strong>Years of Service</strong></span></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\"><strong>Old Rate</strong></span></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\"><strong>As Revised</strong></span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">10th year</span></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">5,000</span></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">10,000</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">15th year</span></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">2,500</span></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">5,000</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">20th year</span></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">2,500</span></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">5,000</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">25th year</span></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">2,500</span></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">5,000</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">30th year</span></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">2,500</span></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">5,000</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">35th year</span></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">2,500</span></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">5,000</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">40th year</span></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">2,500</span></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">5,000</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">At the time of audit, it was revealed that the Institute only provides the loyalty cash award required by COA but have not tried providing any non-monetary awards such as memorabilla/souvenir as required by the MC, aside from the certificate given during their anniversary celebrations.</span></p>', '', ' ', ' ', ' ', '2019-08-15 08:55:28', '2019-08-16 14:50:01', '0', '1', ' ');
