(37, '2', 10, '', '5', 'Finance and Administrative Division (FAD)', ' ', 'Account Classification', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\"><strong>Accounting Entry in recording the P10,000,000 deposits for IGF is not aligned with GAM and UACS Code</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">During the interview with the Accountant, she disclosed that the P10,000,000 annual appropriations was recorded as other investments and marketable securities. It was also confirmed upon checking their Notes to Financial Statements in years 2011-2018, except in 2017 wherein no disclosure was made on the Investment account.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">The balance of the account is increased by the P10,000,000 annual appropriations, interest earnings and repayments from the inventors while decreased by granting of loans and payment of awards and prizes for the winners of the National Invention Contest and Exhibits (NICE). Per verification, they are using the Account Code &ldquo;10203990&rdquo;.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">However, based on Government Accounting Manual (GAM) Volume 3, Account Number 10203990 pertains to &ldquo;Other Investments&rdquo; and not Other Investments and Marketable Securities as used by the Agency.&nbsp; </span></p>', '', ' ', ' ', ' ', '2019-08-16 09:32:45', '2019-08-16 09:32:45', '0', '1', ' ');
