(47, '2', 11, '', '5', 'Finance and Administrative Division (FAD)', ' ', 'Monthly Disbursement Program (MDP', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\"><strong>Timing on depositing the 10,000,000 required allotment for IGF is not aligned with the Monthly Disbursement Program (MDP)</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">Paragraph 2, Section 9, Article V of RA No. 7459 requires that a continuing annual appropriation in the amount not less than Ten Million Pesos (P10,000,000) shall be provided for this purpose (Invention Guarantee Fund) in the annual budget of the Department of Science and Technology (DOST). The Fund shall also be used for special financing programs for Filipino inventions pursuant under this Act.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">Also, National budget Circular No. 573 or the Guidelines on the Release of Funds for FY 2018 dated January 3, 2018 described the Monthly Disbursement Program (MDP) or the Budget Execution Document (BED) No. 3 as the basis for the DBM&rsquo;s release of disbursement authorities including the comprehensive Notice of Cash Allocation (NCA) covering the full year cash requirements of the agency for its regular operating requirements.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">During the interview with the Accountant, it was mentioned that separate NCA was not issued for this purpose. Instead, this is lumped to the monthly NCA received by the Agency. The said 10 million budget for the Fund is also included in the Agency&rsquo;s MDP or BED No. 3 and presented under the Capital Outlay of the Agency Specific Budget.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">Upon comparing the amounts and months showed in their MDP against the monthly deposit to Land Bank for IGF purposes, it was observed that the timing and amount of amount deposited do not tally. As disclosed by the Accountant during the interview, deposits depend on the amount of unutilized NCA at the end of the month. Also, it was noted that 2016-2018 funding for IGF were deposited to Land Bank during the end of each quarter, although their MDP showed amounts for other months. This is one of their strategies to avoid the lapsing of unutilized NCA the end of the quarter. The staggered deposit is stopped once required annual funding is reached. In most months, MDP does not coincide with the actual deposits.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">Table __: Comparison of Monthly Disbursement program and Actual Deposit for the Invention Guarantee Fund (in thousand pesos)</span></p>\r\n<table style=\"border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; height: 2347px;\" border=\"1\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr style=\"height: 97px;\">\r\n<td style=\"width: 25%; height: 97px; text-align: center;\">\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">Year</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 25%; height: 97px; text-align: center;\" colspan=\"2\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">Per MDP</span></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 12.5%; height: 97px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">Actual Deposit for IGF</span></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 12.5%; height: 97px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">Remarks</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style=\"height: 47px;\">\r\n<td style=\"width: 25%; height: 47px; text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td style=\"