(48, '2', 12, '', '5', 'Finance and Administrative Division (FAD)', ' ', 'Updating and Monitoring of Financial Records', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\"><strong>Monitoring Report for Outstanding Loan balances, Collection, Accrued Interest and penalties were not updated</strong></span></p>\r\n<ol style=\"list-style-type: lower-alpha; text-align: justify;\">\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong>Based on the data collection during the audit, the Audit Team was informed that IGF was able to assist thirteen (13) individuals/companies from 2011-2018. As culled from their Statement of Financial Position and Notes to Financial Statements in the years covered by the audit, it was noted that the outstanding balance of the Loans Receivable account amounting to P57,548,426.03 did not move/change in 2011 to 2016. However, upon checking with the General Ledger of their investment account, there are recorded collections from Adela Magdaraog (Universal Fabricators) from years 2011 to 2013 and 2015 as follows:</span>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">Table __: Payments made by Adela Magdaraog (Universal Fabricators)</span></p>\r\n<table style=\"border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%;\" border=\"1\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\"><strong>Date</strong></span></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\"><strong>Reference</strong></span></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\"><strong>Amount</strong></span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">05-10-2011</span></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">2011-05-0658</span></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">&nbsp;10,000.00</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">06-13-2011</span></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">2011-06-0787</span></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">10,000.00</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">11-12-2012</span></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">2012-11-1569</span></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">10,000.00</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">12-28-2012</span></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">2012-12-1873</span></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">&nbsp;10,000.00&nbsp;</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">02-28-2013</span></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">2013-02-0214</span></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">60,000.00</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">06-06-2013</span></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">2013-06-0777</span></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">40,000.00</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">08-06-2013</span></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">2013-08-1096</span></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">20,000.00</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">09-27-2013</span></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">2013-09-1338</span></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">20,000.00</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">08-31-2015</span></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">2015-08-1095</span></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">60,000.00</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">09-30-2015</span></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">2015-09-1381</span></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">60,000.00</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">10-31-2015</span></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">2015-10-1582</span></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">60,000.00</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">11-10-2015</span></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">2015-11-1756</span></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">60,000.00</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">12-10-2015</span></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">2015-12-2064</span></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">70,551.99</span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%;\" colspan=\"2\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\"><strong>Total</strong></span></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\"><strong>490,551.99</strong></span></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">Upon matching with the Loans Receivable Account, it was noted that said collections were not recorded and constantly reporting P310,551.99 Based on their summary records of Loans Receivables, amounts borrowed by Adela Magdaraog was only fully paid in 2017, although their General Ledger showed that a record of full payment prior to this year. Records also showed that receivable from the said inventor only amounts to P310,551.99, not tally with P490,551.99 paid in 2011 to 2013 and 2015. This resulted to an observation there is an under-recording of loans receivable and delayed recording of collections which affects the reliability of this accounts in the year covered. The 2011-2018 balance of loans receivable, per inventor, is attached in Annex I.</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">Moreover, there are discrepancies noted on the 2013 Summary of Loan balances submitted by TAPI and with the Loans Receivable Account disclosed in their 2013 Financial Statements. Based on the summary report, principal account of loan as of December 31, 2013 amounted to P58,750,140.14 (if recomputed, P57,247,799.24) while the Statement of Financial Positions a 2013 outstanding balance of P57,548,426.03 or a variance amounting to P1,201,714.11. The compared reports are attached in Annex F and J.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">Referring to their 2018 Notes to Financial Statements, it was disclosed that 2018 Loans Receivable Balance amounted to P57,120,399.14 from the original amount of P57,237,874.05. this showed variance of P117,474.91. This is already discussed with the Accountant and explained that there may be payments received from the borrowers. However, upon checking their records and with the reports provided by Land Bank, there were no collections made in 2018.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">Loans granted to inventors earns an interest rate of 6% and penalty of 24% per annum in case of late payment. However, the latest monitoring report presented during the audit was as of December 31, 2013. The said report showed total accrued interest of P38,337,820.01 and penalties of P153,473,705.55 or a total amount of P191,811,525.56. This accounts for almost 335% of the P57,247,79924 principal amount as of 2013.</span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">Also, accounting books showed that there was no recorded interest receivables and penalties since 2014. It was only on September 30, 2018 that the interest income and penalties computed as of December 31, 2013 was recorded through JEV No. 2018-09-1067. Accrued interest and penalties from 2014 to present was still not computed and recorded as of the time of audit. Copy of the Journal Entry Voucher is attached in Annex K.</span></p>', '', ' ', ' ', ' ', '2019-08-16 11:14:01', '2019-08-19 15:59:45', '0', '3', ' ');
