(50, '2', 13, '', '5', 'Finance and Administrative Division (FAD)', ' ', 'Internal Guidelines of NICE Prizes', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\"><strong>Policies and Guidelines on the Increased amounts of NICE Prizes in 2016 and 2018 were not available during the time of audit</strong></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">Section 4, Article 2 or Cash Rewards provision of RA 7459 provides that <em>Presidential awards for inventions consisting of Cash Rewards shall be granted to patented inventions in the Philippines to be chosen by a screening committee with members consisting of technical representatives from the Department of Science and Technology, the Filipino Inventors Society, and the Department of Environment and Natural Resources.</em></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">It is further specified that outstanding inventors shall be divided into four (4) categories with the corresponding cash rewards as follows:</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\">Table __: Awards and Prizes for Outstanding Inventors</span></p>\r\n<table style=\"border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%;\" border=\"1\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\"><strong>Category</strong></span></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;\"><strong>Award</strong></span></td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%; text-align: center;\"><span